      "cookedHtml": "<p>Experience a seamless workflow with <a href=\"https://www.make.com/en/register?pc=msquare\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Make.com</a> (Integromat), connecting <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> with QuickBooks! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/robot.png?v=12\" title=\":robot:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":robot:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/briefcase.png?v=12\" title=\":briefcase:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":briefcase:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/credit_card.png?v=12\" title=\":credit_card:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":credit_card:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/chart_with_upwards_trend.png?v=12\" title=\":chart_with_upwards_trend:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":chart_with_upwards_trend:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Workflow:<br />\nThe automation effortlessly handles purchase orders, bill creation, and vendor management based on dynamic <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> board info. <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/briefcase.png?v=12\" title=\":briefcase:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":briefcase:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/credit_card.png?v=12\" title=\":credit_card:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":credit_card:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/globe_with_meridians.png?v=12\" title=\":globe_with_meridians:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":globe_with_meridians:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Dynamic Vendor Handling (QuickBook):<br />\nIf a vendor exists, it generates a bill; if not, it creates a new vendor and generates a bill for the fresh entry. <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>Welcome to a world where automation transforms tasks into triumphs. <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/star2.png?v=12\" title=\":star2:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":star2:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/7/3/73623be8d8916fadeee0ae158e916d320e12c4f2.jpeg\" title=\"ltstt\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/7/3/73623be8d8916fadeee0ae158e916d320e12c4f2_2_690x252.jpeg\" alt=\"ltstt\" width=\"690\" height=\"252\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">ltstt</span><span class=\"informations\">1144×418 26.7 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p><strong>If you need any implementation support kindly contact us</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://calendly.com/msquarepro/meeting\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">MSquare Support</a><br />\nVisit us <a href=\"https://www.msquare.pro/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">here</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqidlIIwbejxZmRUWBICcjQ\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Youtube Channel</a></p>"
